Lazy morning? This brunch or as breakie has your back!
Spinach, eggs, protein, and flavors….this is your sign to stop skipping breakfast! 

Quickest recipe: 

•Frozen spinach sautéed in olive oil + salt + pepper
•3 eggs scramble with salt, pepper & garlic powder
•Mix with spinach after cooking
•Spread labneh or cream cheese on toast, add chicken salami + spinach egg scramble 

Done. Nutritious, filling, and ready in minutes!

Tip: Frozen spinach is a lifesaver..Unlike fresh spinach that loses nutrients in the fridge…. frozen ones retain more value and need a smaller quantity for a bigger impact. Save time and get the goodness!
